          marked it as wish-list




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer994956610" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10574529390718263482"><a href='http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_slatest/2017/03/14/how_is_steve_bannon_getting_away_with_this.html' rel='nofollow noopener'>Steve Bannon endorses this book</a><br/><br/>In the same way I read the Protocols of the Elders of Zion and Mein Kampf etc etc I think I need to be aware what is contained in this book, although it must of fallen on commonsense ears as only 124 people have rated it since its publication in 1973.<br/><br/>Pre-reading, I go with <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/937400441?book_show_action=false&amp;page=1' rel='nofollow noopener'>Hadrian</a><br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1390143800p2/2192.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/> <i>“It is the mark of an educated mind to be able to entertain a thought without accepting it.”</i> ― Aristotle, Metaphysics</span>
  <span id="freeText10574529390718263482" style="display:none"><a href="http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_slatest/2017/03/14/how_is_steve_bannon_getting_away_with_this.html" rel="nofollow noopener">Steve Bannon endorses this book</a><br><br>In the same way I read the Protocols of the Elders of Zion and Mein Kampf etc etc I think I need to be aware what is contained in this book, although it must of fallen on commonsense ears as only 124 people have rated it since its publication in 1973.<br><br>Pre-reading, I go with <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/937400441?book_show_action=false&amp;page=1" rel="nofollow noopener">Hadrian</a><br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1390143800p2/2192.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"> <i>“It is the mark of an educated mind to be able to entertain a thought without accepting it.”</i> ― Aristotle, Metaphysics</span>
