      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/201383.Jean_Raspail">About Jean Raspail</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/201383.Jean_Raspail"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1442093756p3/201383.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/201383.Jean_Raspail">Jean Raspail
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
47
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer664236264718373328">Jean Raspail was a French author, traveler and explorer. He was best known for his controversial 1973 novel, <i>The Camp of the Saints</i>, which is about mass third world immigration to Europe.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

